title: Microsoft.SQL.Server.2008.Developer.Edititon.DVD.iso
description:
Another deliberate187 release.  This is an unmodified Microsoft SQL Server 2008 Developer Edition ISO.  It needs no CD key and is full version.

Check the .nfo for details, I really doubt you'll need them though.  If you know what this program is and does, chances are you already know what you're doing.

Warning:  This is 3GB.  Yes, it IS huge.  If you have a DreamSpark account, you can download this EXACT SAME ISO in half the time.  You've been warned.

I'm not going through the bullshit of finding out the system requirements.  All I know is you need Windows XP SP2 or later and a fairly decent processor with a good amount of memory.  Good enough?  Good.  It's 4AM.

That said, here it is.  As promised.
